sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Data as Data Collection
    participant Sentiment as Sentiment Analysis
    participant Strategy as Trading Strategy
    participant Viz as Visualization
    
    User->>Data: Configure data sources
    Data->>Data: Connect to APIs
    Data->>User: Confirm data access
    
    User->>Data: Fetch market data
    Data->>User: Return price data
    
    User->>Data: Fetch text data
    Data->>User: Return social/news data
    
    User->>Sentiment: Configure LLM settings
    Sentiment->>Sentiment: Initialize analyzer
    
    User->>Sentiment: Process text data
    Sentiment->>Sentiment: Run LLM analysis
    Sentiment->>User: Return sentiment scores
    
    User->>Strategy: Define strategy parameters
    Strategy->>Strategy: Initialize backtester
    
    User->>Strategy: Run backtest
    Strategy->>Strategy: Calculate performance
    Strategy->>User: Return results & statistics
    
    User->>Viz: Create visualization
    Viz->>Viz: Generate dashboard
    Viz->>User: Display interactive charts
    
    User->>Strategy: Refine strategy
    Strategy->>User: Updated performance metrics
    
    User->>Viz: Export results
    Viz->>User: Save reports & charts 